Chunghwa Telecom to Spend NT$3 BLN on 5-Star Hotel, Times Says

-- B y   A n d r e a   W o n g
-- 
2011-02-14T23:14:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-14/chunghwa-telecom-to-spend-nt-3-bln-on-5-star-hotel-times-says.html
 Chunghwa Telecom Co. will spend
NT$3 billion ($102.2 million) to build a five-star hotel with
more than 100 rooms near Jinghua street, the Commercial Times
reported, citing people in the industry it didn’t identify. The
government is planning to develop the neighborhood as the city’s
financial centre, the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
